CGI-Template version 0.01
=========================

CGI::Template is an easy to use and intuitive template system for Perl 
web application development.

This is the initial version of CGI::Template.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other modules and libraries.

